Base table or view not found: 1932 Table 
'sistema_gestiona.usuarios' doesn't exist in engine in 
E:\xampp\htdocs\gestiona\core\Auth.php:39 Stack trace: 
#0 E:\xampp\htdocs\gestiona\core\Auth.php(39): PDO-
>prepare('\n SE...') #1 
